cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with super-resolution (SR) applications using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel network utilizing maxout units (MU) and investigates their effects, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with image processing and analysis, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
